Hello! I was looking at the course guide and was wondering if the professor for EE C128 is known. I know Professor Sojoudi was originally listed to teach it, but now I'm not seeing any professor name listed and am slightly worried that the course won't be offered, since it wasn't held this fall as well. It would be great to receive assurance that the course will be held/who the professor is if possible, as it's a really foundational and important class for EE work.

Thank you!
